video_title: Why You Choose The Wrong People
transcript:
imagine for a moment that growing up the
only movies you ever saw were horror
movies you had no idea that any other
type of movie even existed so now as an
adult when you come across a horror
movie there's some reassurance in the
familiarity of that this is your only
template for how things are supposed to
go and it's much the same in
relationships we seek The Familiar so if
you only have experience of feeling
unsafe growing up why would you expect
anything different as an ad adult so
what may have looked to others like a
poor choice from your perspective maybe
didn't feel like a choice at all
